trans-unit.source: The ForestTrustCollisionException class exception is thrown when a trust collision occurs during a trust relationship management request.
trans-unit.target: ForestTrustCollisionException klassen undantag genereras när förtroendet kollision uppstår under en betrodd relation management begäran.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionException"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionException"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionException"></xref> class with a specified error message.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionException"> </xref> klass med ett angivet meddelande.

trans-unit.source: A message that describes the error.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionException"></xref> class, using the specified serialization information and streaming context.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionException"> </xref> klassen med hjälp av angivna serialiseringsinformation och strömning kontext.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionException"></xref> class with a specified error message and an underlying exception object.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionException"> </xref> klass med ett angivet meddelande och ett underliggande undantag-objekt.

trans-unit.source: A message that describes the error.
An <xref:System.Exception> object that contains underlying exception information.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionException"></xref> class with a specified error message, an underlying exception object, and a specified <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollisionCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionException"> </xref> klass med ett angivet meddelande, ett underliggande undantag objekt och en angiven <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollisionCollection"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: A message that describes the error.
An <xref:System.Exception> object that contains underlying exception information.

A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollisionCollection"></xref> object that contains one or more <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision"></xref> objects that describe the trust relationship collision errors.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollisionCollection"> </xref> objekt som innehåller en eller flera <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision"> </xref> objekt som beskriver förtroende relationen kollision felen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollisionCollection"></xref> object that contains the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision"></xref> objects that describe the trust relationship collision errors.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollisionCollection"> </xref> objekt som innehåller den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision"> </xref> objekt som beskriver förtroende relationen kollision felen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollisionCollection"></xref> that contains one or more <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision"></xref> objects that describe the trust relationship collision errors.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollisionCollection"> </xref> som innehåller en eller flera <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision"> </xref> objekt som beskriver förtroende relationen kollision felen.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> object with information about the exception.
trans-unit.target: Anger den <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> objekt med information om undantaget.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> object that contains serialized object data about the exception being thrown.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> objekt som innehåller serialiseras objektdata om undantag som genereras.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext> object that contains contextual information about the source or destination.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>objekt som innehåller detaljerad information om käll- och målservrar.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>
